data.description: Bring your picky buyers to see this! Sophisticated 3/2.5 on premiere corner lot . Gorgeous kitchen with granite counter tops,stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, tile backsplash. Master bath features double vanities, separate shower, & garden tub. Home has 3 living areas, huge closets, wood & ceramic tile flooring. Relax in the X-lrg back yard with Oak trees while sitting on the deck. It has a full yard sprinkler system,& just minutes away from the community park. 30 min notice please (Dogs)
